Comment: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EN,,0,0,0,,--------------------TEXT-EN--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Whether you're 16 or 40
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:04.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Coming out is never easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.66,EN,,0,0,0,,There's never a right time to come out as the only perfect time is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:10.64,EN,,0,0,0,,When you feel safe and comfortable with your own self
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:14.13,EN,,0,0,0,,Have you figured out that you're a part of the LGBT community
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:15.97,EN,,0,0,0,,but you're not sure how to tell people about it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:20.87,EN,,0,0,0,,Here are 8 things you need to know before coming out of the closet
Comment: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:25.81,EN,,0,0,0,,1. It doesn't have to be perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:25.81,EN,,0,0,0,,It's okay to feel anxious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:30.87,EN,,0,0,0,,It's perfectly normal to feel nervous or even anxiety when you think about coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:35.04,EN,,0,0,0,,The thought of making the announcement itself is what scares you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.51,EN,,0,0,0,,just remember that coming out doesn't have to be a grand event
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:43.27,EN,,0,0,0,,Some people may feel empowered by coming out parties and Facebook posts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.85,EN,,0,0,0,,but it can be as intimate as you need it to be
Comment: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:52.47,EN,,0,0,0,,2. You don't have to do it alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:52.07,EN,,0,0,0,,Coming out doesn't have to be something you have to handle on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:55.34,EN,,0,0,0,,It's perfectly okay to have a friend or a loved one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.64,EN,,0,0,0,,someone you've already come out to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.90,EN,,0,0,0,,to accompany you in situations that may make you especially anxious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:03.97,EN,,0,0,0,,This can include telling your parents
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:07.09,EN,,0,0,0,,extended family or even a group of friends
Comment: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.85,EN,,0,0,0,,3. Choose the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:12.97,EN,,0,0,0,,When coming out to close friends and family for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.84,EN,,0,0,0,,it helps to have their undivided attention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.20,EN,,0,0,0,,before bringing up something so important
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.31,EN,,0,0,0,,it's not the best idea to come out during major events
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.46,EN,,0,0,0,,like weddings or baby showers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:28.31,EN,,0,0,0,,or while the person you're talking to has their minds occupied with other activities
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:33.35,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0}It's also probably not a great idea to bring home a brand new partner to shock your parents with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:37.16,EN,,0,0,0,,Coming out can be an emotional time for every party evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:41.96,EN,,0,0,0,,So it's important to give the person you're talking to attention and private time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:44.14,EN,,0,0,0,,to help them internalize what you're telling them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:50.68,EN,,0,0,0,,Before we continue, we'd like to thank our partner TUSI cosmetics for sponsoring this video
Comment: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:59.97,EN,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.10,EN,,0,0,0,,4. Don't put yourself at risk
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:31.31,EN,,0,0,0,,There are situations in which coming out can mean jeopardizing your own safety
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:37.81,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.8}Remember your safety must always come first if you fear that coming out to someone could harm you in any way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:39.38,EN,,0,0,0,,Socially or even physically,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.64,EN,,0,0,0,,then don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:45.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, there are people that may not be accepting of you coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.78,EN,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean that you have to live the rest of your life in the closet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.28,EN,,0,0,0,,If being openly LGBTQ at home is not a safe option for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:56.93,EN,,0,0,0,,or even if you feel ostracized or shamed where you live
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.63,EN,,0,0,0,,It's important to look for support and comfort elsewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:05.72,EN,,0,0,0,,Search for any LGBTQ friendly community programs or alliances near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:09.32,EN,,0,0,0,,or speak to a counselor to discuss your possible options
Comment: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:16.52,EN,,0,0,0,,5. Throw away your expectations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.18,EN,,0,0,0,,People's first reactions may not be the ones you wanted or expected
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:19.31,EN,,0,0,0,,This is a big part of your life that you're opening them up to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.31,EN,,0,0,0,,and everyone reacts differently to news this big
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:29.31,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1.9}some people may be completely shocked while others may need some time alone to digest the information
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:34.20,EN,,0,0,0,,Others may have already seen some clues that you were LGBTQ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.30,EN,,0,0,0,,and may tell you that they had a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.49,EN,,0,0,0,,Some people may treat the topic very casually
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.62,EN,,0,0,0,,as if it was just some cool thing about you that they didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.67,EN,,0,0,0,,whatever their response
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.35,EN,,0,0,0,,try not to judge them and be patient with how they handle your news
Comment: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:53.10,EN,,0,0,0,,6. A true family bond can't be broken by sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.48,EN,,0,0,0,,Don't be so hard on your parents
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Some parents know their children are queer before they themselves do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:05.35,EN,,0,0,0,,But other parents may have a different life for their children planned out in their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:10.27,EN,,0,0,0,,In their minds, you're goingt to marry a cisgendered person of the opposite sex
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.97,EN,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have children naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:16.86,EN,,0,0,0,,You would never know the hatefulness and fear of homophobia or transphobia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.98,EN,,0,0,0,,While the world still has a long way to go in the equality department
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:24.09,EN,,0,0,0,,you parants need help to understand that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.52,EN,,0,0,0,,who you've always been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.97,EN,,0,0,0,,and your life for the most part doesn't have to change
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.98,EN,,0,0,0,,Be open with them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.76,EN,,0,0,0,,explain your feelings to them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:35.14,EN,,0,0,0,,don't be upset if they react with sadness or disappointment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:39.97,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0}Sometimes we get caught up in thinking that it's everyone else's job to try to see things our way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.83,EN,,0,0,0,,but your parents aren't perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.81,EN,,0,0,0,,they need help understanding too
Comment: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:48.06,EN,,0,0,0,,7. Prepare yourself for questions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.06,EN,,0,0,0,,Be open to questions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:52.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Know that people you came out to may ask questions lots and lots of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:56.18,EN,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they may not always feel appropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:59.05,EN,,0,0,0,,In fact, they might feel tad invasive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.83,EN,,0,0,0,,But they're just curious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.93,EN,,0,0,0,,They're just trying to gain an understanding of your newly proclaimed identity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:10.64,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0}Note that while it's important to be open and willing to educate those close to you about yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.83,EN,,0,0,0,,You also don't have to feel like you need to explain everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.51,EN,,0,0,0,,There are some things you would rather keep private
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.02,EN,,0,0,0,,There are others we don't always know the answers to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Just be patient
Comment: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.31,EN,,0,0,0,,8. Coming out never ends
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.97,EN,,0,0,0,,Heterosexual people don't have to walk into a room and shout
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.62,EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm straight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.65,EN,,0,0,0,,and you shouldn't have to either
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:33.81,EN,,0,0,0,,We often don't understand how much our sexual and gender identities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.17,EN,,0,0,0,,play into our everyday lives until we realize we're queer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:41.18,EN,,0,0,0,,Do you talk about your girlfriend when all the other girls in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:44.17,EN,,0,0,0,,are discussing funny things that their boyfriend said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:51.28,EN,,0,0,0,,Whether you decide to disclose your LGBTQ identity or not is up to you and your comfort level
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:56.70,EN,,0,0,0,,It might always be a little nerve-racking to let people find out that you're LGBTQ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.19,EN,,0,0,0,,but it gets easier every time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.51,EN,,0,0,0,,Coming out can be daunting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:08.04,EN,,0,0,0,,and sometimes it feels like there are a hundred reasons why we just shouldn't do it at all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.59,EN,,0,0,0,,But once you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:13.28,EN,,0,0,0,,there are a thousand reasons why coming out can be amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.51,EN,,0,0,0,,Coming out is never easy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:19.31,EN,,0,0,0,,The most important part is being confident and true to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:22.83,EN,,0,0,0,,Do you have any coming-out advice that you'd like to give?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:26.64,EN,,0,0,0,,Let your fellow readers know in the comment section down below
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.29,EN,,0,0,0,,National Coming Out Day is October 11th
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.72,EN,,0,0,0,,and it's been around since 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching
Comment: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,--------------------TEXT-CN--------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.14,CN,,0,0,0,,不论你是16岁或是40岁
Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.14,0:00:04.34,CN,,0,0,0,,出柜从不是一件简单的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.66,CN,,0,0,0,,不存在一个正确的时间出柜
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.66,0:00:10.64,CN,,0,0,0,,因为唯一的好时机，就是当你对自己感到安全与舒适的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.91,0:00:14.13,CN,,0,0,0,,你有没有过意识到自己是性少数群体的一员
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.13,0:00:15.97,CN,,0,0,0,,但是你却不知道该如何跟别人说起这件事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.51,0:00:20.87,CN,,0,0,0,,下面我们将介绍8件你在出柜之前必须知道的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.39,0:00:25.81,CN,,0,0,200,,{\bord0}1.出柜不需要一切都完美
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.93,0:00:25.81,CN,,0,0,0,,感到焦虑是很正常的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.81,0:00:30.87,CN,,0,0,0,,当你想要出柜时，感到紧张甚至焦虑是完全正常的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.23,0:00:35.04,CN,,0,0,0,,一想到要宣布这件事你就害怕
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.51,CN,,0,0,0,,只要记住，出柜不一定是件大事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.93,0:00:43.27,CN,,0,0,0,,有些人会觉得举办出柜派对或者在脸书上发帖显得更有力量
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.85,CN,,0,0,0,,但是你想要多私密地出柜就可以多私密
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.52,0:00:52.47,CN,,0,0,300,,{\bord0}2.你不需要一个人完成
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.83,0:00:52.07,CN,,0,0,0,,出柜不一定是你必须自己处理的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.47,0:00:55.34,CN,,0,0,0,,有一个朋友或者是爱人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.64,CN,,0,0,0,,一个你已经向他/她出柜的人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.90,CN,,0,0,0,,陪伴你度过那些会你觉得特别焦虑的时期是很好的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.90,0:01:03.97,CN,,0,0,0,,这些焦虑的时期可以包括告诉你的父母
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.97,0:01:07.09,CN,,0,0,0,,告诉大家庭甚至是一帮朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.85,CN,,0,0,200,,{\bord0\fad(200,0)}3.选择一个合适的时机
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.85,0:01:12.97,CN,,0,0,0,,当你第一次向亲密的朋友或者家人出柜时
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.84,CN,,0,0,0,,在提出这么重要的事情之前
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.20,CN,,0,0,0,,他们对你全心全意的关注很重要
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.31,CN,,0,0,0,,在重大事件时出柜不是一个好主意
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.46,CN,,0,0,0,,比如婚礼、迎婴聚会
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.46,0:01:28.31,CN,,0,0,0,,或者跟你说话的人脑子正在想其他事情
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.31,0:01:33.35,CN,,0,0,0,,带一个新伴侣回家让你的父母受惊吓可能也不是个好主意
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.35,0:01:37.16,CN,,0,0,0,,对每一个派对来说，出柜都是一个激动人心的时刻
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.16,0:01:41.96,CN,,0,0,0,,所以给予与你对话的人关注和私人时间
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.96,0:01:44.14,CN,,0,0,0,,来帮助他们消化你所说的事情是很重要的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.42,0:01:50.68,CN,,0,0,0,,在我们继续之前，我们要感谢我们的合作伙伴图思化妆品对本期视频的赞助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:02:24.39,CN,,0,0,0,,广告时间 可以跳到2.25s看正片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.10,CN,,0,0,360,,{\bord0}4.不要让自己冒险
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.10,0:02:31.31,CN,,0,0,0,,有些情况出柜会意味着危及你的安全
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.31,0:02:37.81,CN,,0,0,0,,记住，如果你担心出柜会让其他人以任何方式伤害你，你的安全必须总是第一位
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.81,0:02:39.38,CN,,0,0,0,,无论是在社交上或者身体上
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.64,CN,,0,0,0,,那就不要出柜！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.10,0:02:45.50,CN,,0,0,0,,不幸的是，有些人可能不接受你出柜
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.78,CN,,0,0,0,,但是这不意味着你要在深柜之中度过余生
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.28,CN,,0,0,0,,如果在家公开性少数身份对你来说不是一个安全的选择
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.28,0:02:56.93,CN,,0,0,0,,或者即使你在你居住的地方感到被排斥或羞耻
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.63,CN,,0,0,0,,那么在其他地方寻求支持和安慰是很重要的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.04,0:03:05.72,CN,,0,0,0,,在你周围寻找任何性少数友好的社区项目或联盟
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.72,0:03:09.32,CN,,0,0,0,,或者和顾问讨论你可能的选择
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.81,0:03:16.52,CN,,0,0,250,,{\bord0}5.摒弃你的任何期待
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.18,CN,,0,0,0,,人们的第一反应可能不会是你想要或是期待的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.18,0:03:19.31,CN,,0,0,0,,这是向他们展示的你人生的很大一部分
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.31,CN,,0,0,0,,每个人会对这么大的消息有不同的反应
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.81,0:03:29.31,CN,,0,0,0,,一些人可能会彻底震惊，而另一些人可能需要一些时间来消化信息
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.22,0:03:34.20,CN,,0,0,0,,还有些人可能已经看到一些你是性少数人的迹象
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.30,CN,,0,0,0,,可能会告诉你他们的感受
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.49,CN,,0,0,0,,有些人很平常地对待这个话题
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.62,CN,,0,0,0,,好像这是一些不为他们所知的你身上很酷的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.67,CN,,0,0,0,,不论他们回应什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.35,CN,,0,0,0,,尽量不要去评判他们，对他们如何处理你的消息要有耐心
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.77,0:03:53.10,CN,,0,0,230,,{\bord0}6.一个真正牢固的家庭纽带是不会被性别取向打破的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.48,CN,,0,0,0,,不要对你的家长太过苛刻
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.86,CN,,0,0,0,,有些父母在孩子自己意识到之前就知道他们是同性恋
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.28,0:04:05.35,CN,,0,0,0,,但是其他家长在脑海中可能对孩子有截然不同的规划
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.35,0:04:10.27,CN,,0,0,0,,他们认为，你会和一个异性结婚
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.97,CN,,0,0,0,,你将自然而然的有个孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.97,0:04:16.86,CN,,0,0,0,,你永远不会知道对同性恋或变性人的憎恶和恐惧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.98,CN,,0,0,0,,然而这个世界在平等方面还有很长的路要走
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.98,0:04:24.09,CN,,0,0,0,,你的家长需要帮助你了解你是谁
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.52,CN,,0,0,0,,你一直以来是谁
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.97,CN,,0,0,0,,你人生的很大一部分不需要做改变
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.98,CN,,0,0,0,,对他们坦诚一些吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.76,CN,,0,0,0,,向他们诉说你的感受
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.76,0:04:35.14,CN,,0,0,0,,如果他们的回应是悲伤或是失望，不要感到沮丧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.14,0:04:39.97,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候我们会因为认为别人需要从我们角度思考问题而感到困扰
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.83,CN,,0,0,0,,但是你的父母也不是完美的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.81,CN,,0,0,0,,他们也需要理解啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.81,0:04:48.06,CN,,0,0,350,,{\bord0}7.做好应对质疑的准备
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.06,CN,,0,0,0,,乐意应对质疑
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.06,0:04:52.86,CN,,0,0,0,,要知道，你的出柜对象可能会问你很多问题
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.32,0:04:56.18,CN,,0,0,0,,他们可能会觉得不合时宜
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.18,0:04:59.05,CN,,0,0,0,,实际上，他们还可能觉得有点冒犯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.83,CN,,0,0,0,,其实他们只是好奇
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.93,CN,,0,0,0,,他们只是试图理解你的新宣布的身份
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.31,0:05:10.64,CN,,0,0,0,,请注意，尽管乐意去向身边人展现你自己是很重要的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.83,CN,,0,0,0,,你并不需要解释所有事情
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.51,CN,,0,0,0,,有些事情你愿意保密
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.02,CN,,0,0,0,,还有些事情我们也不知道答案是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.74,CN,,0,0,0,,要有耐心
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.31,CN,,0,0,350,,{\bord0}8.出柜无止境
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.97,CN,,0,0,0,,异性恋的人不需要在房间里走来走去喊叫着
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.62,CN,,0,0,0,,嘿！我是直的！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.65,CN,,0,0,0,,你也不需要这样做
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.97,0:05:33.81,CN,,0,0,0,,我们总是在意识到我们是同性恋之后
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.17,CN,,0,0,0,,才感受到性取向在生活中有多么重要
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.68,0:05:41.18,CN,,0,0,0,,当屋里的其他女生都在讨论她们男友说了什么玩笑话时
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.18,0:05:44.17,CN,,0,0,0,,你会说起自己的女友吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.95,0:05:51.28,CN,,0,0,0,,你是否决定公开你的LGBTQ身份取决于你自己和你的舒适程度
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.72,0:05:56.70,CN,,0,0,0,,被别人发现你是性少数群体可能会使人心烦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.19,CN,,0,0,0,,但是一次一次以后这将变得容易起来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.51,CN,,0,0,0,,出柜或许很劝退
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.51,0:06:08.04,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候，我们会觉得有一百个理由让我们根本不应该这么做
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.59,CN,,0,0,0,,但是一旦你准备好了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.59,0:06:13.28,CN,,0,0,0,,将会有一千个理由告诉我们出柜是很不错的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.51,CN,,0,0,0,,出柜从不是一个简单的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.51,0:06:19.31,CN,,0,0,0,,最重要的是自信、真实地对待自己
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.64,0:06:22.83,CN,,0,0,0,,你有没有与出柜相关的建议想分享给大家呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.83,0:06:26.64,CN,,0,0,0,,请在下面的评论区告诉你的读者朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.29,CN,,0,0,0,,全国出柜日是10月11日
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.72,CN,,0,0,0,,从1988年就开始了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.72,0:06:41.14,CN,,0,0,0,,感谢观看
